snippet.title: Shufflepuck Cantina Deluxe VR
snippet.description:
Shufflepuck Cantina Deluxe VR: The first complete game available for Virtual reality!
Buy it on steam ! : http://store.steampowered.com/app/259510
- Head tracking at its best ! (DK2 only)
- Oculus auto detection on launch!
- Complete VR user interfaces !
- No motion sickness!
- Compatible with all oculus rift devices DK1 and DK2 +

Twitter and facebook :
http://facebook.aghartastudio.com
http://twitter.aghartastudio.com

NOTE : No cats were harmed ^^
